title: Cammerlander Market Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tapas bar next to Markethall and bus stops. On the menu is a surprising vegan section with around 4 vegan mains (pizza, ramen, lasagna, a bean dish) plus a couple of starters, and a pudding.
